title: Episode 36: How To Become Radically Confident with Author and Entrepreneur Lisa Bilyeu
description:
In this episode, Nicole chats with friend and fellow author, Lisa Bilyeu. Lisa is the co-founder of Quest Nutrition and the founder of Women of Impact. Her new book “Radical Confidence” is a must read for anyone looking to be an empowered creator of their life. This episode was a blast to record and there are tons of gems for you all.
